simple_means.memory_skill: in 加以… + quir 寻求；获得 + e → 加以询问 → 询问

ex.chText: 你最好问一下去飞机场怎么走。
ex.enText: You'd better ask someone the way to the airport.

ex.chText: 我可以问你一个问题吗？
ex.enText: May I ask you a question?

synonyms.bx: 最普通用词，指提出问题让人回答，多用于口语中。

ex.enText: We inquired about the way to the station.
The police inquired at the next door.

ex.chText: 她询问国家图书馆何时开门。
ex.enText: She inquired when the national library would open.

synonyms.bx: 较正式用词，指为了解真实情况而详细询问。

ex.chText: 他询问她是否参加聚会。
ex.enText: He queried/asked if she would come to the party.

ex.chText: “你们什么时候出发？”汤姆问道。
ex.enText: 'What time are you leaving?' Tom queried/asked.

ex.chText: 她就经济情况向总统提问。
ex.enText: She queried/asked the president about the economic situation.

synonyms.bx: 作此义解时，可与 ask 换用。

ex.enText: The murderer was questioned for 3 hours.

synonyms.bx: 指因感到可疑或为了解情况、弄清究竟而正式地发问，尤指就某一罪案进行盘问。

tr: have a wish or desire to know something
example: He wondered who had built this beautiful church
I asked about their special today
He had to ask directions several times

tr: conduct an inquiry or investigation of
example: The district attorney's office investigated reports of possible irregularities
inquire into the disappearance of the rich old lady

value.def: If you inquire about something, you ask for information about it.

example.ex: 'Who are you?' he enquired of the first man...
I rang up to inquire about train times...
example.tran: 我打了电话查询列车时刻。

example.ex: He inquired whether there had been any messages for him...
example.tran: 他询问是否有留给他的口信。

example.ex: He was so impressed that he inquired the young shepherd's name.
example.tran: 他深受震动，就问那个年轻的牧羊人叫什么名字。

gramarinfo.label: Also V <l>for</l> n, V <l>of</l> n wh, V

value.def: If you inquire into something, you investigate it carefully.

example.ex: Inspectors were appointed to inquire into the affairs of the company.
example.tran: 督查员受委派调查该公司的事务。

rootsaffixes.indicate: = to seek, to obtain 寻求；获得
rootsaffixes.title: quest, quir, quis, quer

partsOfSpeech.dec: ac 加强 + quir 寻求；获得 + e → 获取
acquir〔e〕获得；学识 + ed 表形容词 → 后天习得的
acquire 获取 + ment 表名词 → 获得；学识
ac 加强 + quis 寻求；获得 + itive …的 → 不断寻求 → 贪得的
con 加强 + quer 寻求；获得 → 获得 → 征服
con 共同 + quest 寻求；获得 → 获得 → 征服
dis 分散 + quis 寻求；获得 + ition 行为，状态，结果，由行为产生的事物 → 分开寻问 → 到处问 → 探究
in 加以… + quest 寻求；获得 → 加以询问 → 审问
in 加以… + quir 寻求；获得 + e → 加以询问 → 询问
in 加以… + quis 寻求；获得 + ition，inquire 的名词 → 调查，审问
pre 预先 + requisite 要素，要件 → 先决条件
quer 寻求；获得 + y 表行为 → 寻求答案 → 疑问
quest 寻求；获得 + ion 表名词 → 问题，疑问
re 一再 + quest 寻求；获得 → 因需求而一再要求 → 要求；恳请
re 一再 + quir 寻求；获得 + e → 一再要获得 → 要求 → 强制要求 → 命令
re 一再 + quis 寻求；获得 + ite 表物 → 一再需求的物品 → 必需品 →〔必需品是〕必要的
